{"tid":17760,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"男護性侵27老人 連100歲都不放過","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T10:11:37.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a5e811841da86ad02e4d83c27fbb0bcf342d18","tid":17760,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"芬蘭一名24歲男護士利用職務之便，性侵了27名曾經被他照顧過的老人，年齡從74歲~100歲不等，昨日他遭判9年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報導，案情指出，該名男護士在2013~2014年間，在醫院內專門針對患有癡呆、身體殘疾、臥病在床的老人下手，受害者幾乎都是男護士曾經照顧過的病人。而男護士多在病床或廁所作案。法官認為，男護士是有系統性地犯案，因此判處他9年徒刑，更罰他向受害人賠償共1.8萬歐元(約新台幣72萬元)。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"ca38232c95d656c7af5f41313284b6028e4f1471","tid":17760,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"快點強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4a92a55135ef0642823c59e7eaff6277220764","tid":17760,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"少女我唔鋤愛阿婆"},{"pid":"4438e479735a8787bb61bca59e028bd8df320193","tid":17760,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac541113418a7b68067ef9941af987aa34c6628","tid":17760,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"屌點解男護性侵老人 我第一反應係搞阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000c5dc61b8dfaa83db5f3068d8fa7da8efdf398","tid":17760,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"可能佢有風濕，想驅風"},{"pid":"19667a0adbfee2ca2e5474f8c84abb18a5e03bb2","tid":17760,"uid":50166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌點解男護性侵老人 我第一反應係搞阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1"},{"pid":"45be6ccbe31d889d46d20b7acde739